Our Reporter  Not many will think she would hate flying as she regularly flies across the world, performing on different stages. But music diva Tiwa Savage does not like flying. She gave this hint via her Instagram account on Monday. “My heart is actually beating fast because I hate flying,” she wrote as she posted an image, which showed her sitting in what seemed like a private jet.  Due to different reasons, some persons do not like flying. In a subsequent post, the 49-99 crooner displayed her love for Nigerian fashion designers, as she hinted she was wearing a top and skirt designed by Heritage.